        " خَبَرٍ آخَرَ: \"إِنَّ صَلاَتَهُ تُوقَفُ بَيْنَ اَلسَّمَاءِ وَ اَلْأَرْضِ فَإِذَا تَابَ رُدَّتْ عَلَيْهِ وَ قُبِلْتُ مِنْهُ\"."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.4951 - And in another narration:\n\"Indeed, his prayer will be suspended between the sky and the earth. But if he repents, it will be returned to him and accepted from him.\""
        ]
